com.chute.sdk.v2.model

Class PaginationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chute.sdk.v2.model.PaginationModel

  • public class PaginationModel
extends Object
    The PaginationModel class wraps up information about pagination of the response. The response can show total pages, current page, previous page, first page, last page and number of responses per page.
